This is the offical app for Borden Grammar School
Follow the devlopment here on GitHub


-={---------------------------------------}=-
               How to build
1. Create a new android studio project
2. Download this repo to your computer
3. Copy and paste the code into the newly created project

{-Please note it is very unlikely i will merge your changes to main repo}

4. Once done copy and paste back into the orginal clone
5. Then commit and push to my repo